org.netbeans.spi.java.classpath

Class GlobalPathRegistryImplementation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.netbeans.spi.java.classpath.GlobalPathRegistryImplementation

  • public abstract class GlobalPathRegistryImplementation
extends Object
    The SPI interface for the GlobalPathRegistry. Allows different implementations of the GlobalPathRegistry. The first SPI instance registered in the global Lookup is used by the GlobalPathRegistry. Threading: The implementations don't need to be thread safe, synchronization is done by the GlobalPathRegistry.
    Since:
    1.48
